name: Daves Quilling Cards (Small)
description:
6.4 x 8.9cm

Every single one of Quilling Card’s beautiful greeting cards are handcrafted. Rooted in Vietnam, each artist is assigned to a single design, ensuring efficient workflow and consistency in their work, and by extension in the Squirrelz final product. Quilling Card established a cottage industry in Vietnam, working with the deaf and physically disabled while teaching them the skills needed to earn a sustainable living. Friends and family of the creators collect the supplies, and the work itself is completed in their own home and on their own time. Their next mission is to bring Quilling Card, and that same cottage industry, to China. One thing is clear though: quality-wise it’s not a question of ‘if’ but ‘when’!

name: Tote Daves Bag
description:
40x30x13cm

Bags by Somos Design embody the essence of up-cycling; the reinvention of discarded products and breathing new life and purpose into them. Somos Design bags are bright, fun, and made from sturdy recycled tarpaulin sacks, sourced mainly from cement and fish food companies. These sacks are collected from all over South-East Asia, then cleaned and repurposed in Cambodia. Each and every bag is unique and made by talented local artisans. Tatiana & Alasdair founded Somos Design after discovering these exciting resources during a trip to Cambodia. Utilizing the material to their fullest potential, Somos Design bags have a chic and modern look that’s both eye-catching and practical.
